      <title>俄罗斯空袭导致乌克兰北部地区停电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/russian-air-strikes-cause-power-cuts-in-northern-ukraine-regions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国家电网运营商 Ukrenergo 在 Facebook 上表示，俄罗斯导弹和无人机夜间袭击导致乌克兰北部苏梅和哈尔科夫地区的电力供应中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/russian-air-strikes-cause-power-cuts-in-northern-ukraine-regions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 06:14:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列军方要求拉法平民搬出城市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-06/israel-military-asks-rafah-civilians-to-move-out-of-city-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军方表示，正在要求拉法几个地区的平民搬出该市。此举是在哈马斯和以色列在开罗举行的停火谈判似乎陷入僵局之后做出的。保罗·华莱士在彭博电视台进行报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-06/israel-military-asks-rafah-civilians-to-move-out-of-city-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 06:12:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马恒达汽车部门首席执行官谈电动汽车战略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-06/mahindra-auto-division-ceo-on-ev-strategy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Mahindra &amp; Mahindra 汽车部门首席执行官 Nalinikanth Gollagunta 表示，他的公司计划随着时间的推移将印度的电池生产本地化。他在“法国巴黎银行全球电动汽车和移动会议”间隙与斯蒂芬·恩格尔就“彭博亚洲市场”进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-06/mahindra-auto-division-ceo-on-ev-strategy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 05:48:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>KKR 将从 Apax 收购印度医疗设备制造商 Healthium</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/kkr-to-acquire-indian-medical-device-maker-healthium-from-apax</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR&amp; Co. 正在从私募股权公司 Apax Partners 手中收购总部位于班加罗尔的医疗器械制造商 Healthium Medtech Ltd.，这是印度对全球投资者吸引力不断增强的另一个例子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/kkr-to-acquire-indian-medical-device-maker-healthium-from-apax</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 05:40:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纵目CEO谈自动驾驶发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-06/zongmu-ceo-on-autonomous-driving-development-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纵目科技创始人兼首席执行官唐锐讨论了纵目科技在自动驾驶技术竞争日趋激烈的情况下脱颖而出的战略。他在“法国巴黎银行全球电动汽车和移动会议”间隙与斯蒂芬·恩格尔就“彭博社：中国秀”进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-06/zongmu-ceo-on-autonomous-driving-development-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 05:35:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿拉伯提高油价，油价在一周下跌后上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于沙特阿拉伯连续第三个月上调亚洲原油价格，油价在每周下跌后上涨，表明对欧佩克+卡特尔削减供应的前景充满信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 23:28:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中国股市上涨，欧洲股市将上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/asian-stocks-eye-positive-start-as-china-returns-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股指期货上涨，表明股市将追随亚洲和美国股市的上涨，此前美国非农就业数据弱于预期，重新引发了对美联储降息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/asian-stocks-eye-positive-start-as-china-returns-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 22:32:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
